    "summary": "Advocate emphasizes LullAI's potential to maintain parent-child bonds through AI voice technology, highlighting strong technical implementation, clear vision, and significant social impact. Key strengths include addressing modern parenting challenges and having a comprehensive roadmap. Critic raises concerns about psychological effects, over-reliance on AI, privacy issues, and technical limitations, noting heavy dependence on third-party APIs and lack of proven research backing.",

